messages.message: The listing prices shown represent the first and last listing price RP Data recorded in the advertising campaign for the property. In some instances we may have derived the price from the advertisement text. Where we have been unable to derive the price from the advertisement text (for example "Auctions"), the discounting calculations are unavailable.
